 idea in defining it is the\nsame as in Seidel's construction for Fukaya categories of Lefschetz fibrations\nand in Abouzaid-Seidel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2019 16:27:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Mar 2020 15:02:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2020 23:36:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-24"}
