E-driven shock and a preceding ejecta\nsignificantly enhanced the preexisting southward magnetic fields and gave rise\nto a severe complex geomagnetic storm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2019 01:00:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
