rd joint DICE-FOPARA workshop at ETAPS 2019 follows the successful\nexperiences of co-location of DICE-FOPARA at ETAPS 2015 in London and ETAPS\n2017 in Uppsala.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2019 04:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
