d datasets as well as gender-separated datasets improve\ntrait prediction by up to 17%. We unpack differences in personality models\nacross the five countries, highlight the most predictive data categories\n(location, noise, unlocks, accelerometer), and provide takeaways to\ntechnologists and social scientists interested in passive personality\nassessment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2019 12:56:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
